data.description: Sought-after St James Golf Club is a resort-style gated community, home to The Champion Turf Golf Club links-style, public golf course. Situated on a prime location the home boasts diagonally laid tile enhancing the elegant main living areas, vaulted ceilings, open floorplan and kitchen w/breakfast nook, island, granite counters, stainless-steel appliances and adjacent family room. Primary suite boasts walk-in closets, en suite w/dual sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. Partially covered screen-enclosed patio offers a perfect spot to relax w/captivating views of the golf course. SJGC amenities incl. community pool w/spa, clubhouse, fitness center, bocce court, volleyball, tennis, basketball and tot lot, making this an idyllic retreat for those seeking serenity and active lifestyle.
